Author: Michael Royster
Email: micaher@okstate.edu
Description:
    This program is a simple calculator that performs integer operations.
    Add, subtract, multiply, and integer divide.
    This program also supports a squaring function and the ability to
    flip the sign of the current number.
    The user cannot enter numbers greater than 8 digits.
    The chk button prints the values of the memory holding previous
    numbers and the oprator to the command line.